latestPosts.caption:
Moments from each month that I’ll always remember: 

January: 
Bought my first ever camera & started my YT journey 📷 

February; 
Went on a brand trip for the launch of @thesanctuarykitchengoa and met the lovely @sarahtodd 🩷

March: 
I had been grappling with getting help with work for a while and March was the month when I finally got a manager and it’s honestly helped ease my work load so much!! This photo was taken right before our first meeting 

April: 
Made monthly breakfast dates a thing @parans @vami_s 

May: 
Shot a Mother’s Day campaign for the first time ever with mama for @clinique_in 🩷

June: 
Discovered @journal.bombay and little did we know it would become our forever favourite place to go to 

July: 
@thepostscriptco a year filled with highs and lows - but so proud of everything we’ve achieved 🥹

August: 
I started lifting heavily toward the end of the year and could see some muscle development 💪 

September: 
Made it to beautiful Amsterdam 🥰🥰🥰

October: 
Not a great month, we got some news that shook us but I remember showing up this day for an event even though I didn’t feel like it 

November: 
Treated ourselves a little to our dream coffee machine 🤗

December: 
Right after we saw @maroon5 live 🩷

What a year you’ve been, 2024, here’s to 2025 🥂
